{"tid":1788952,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"撐警怡和子公司金門建築被指拖糧 13工友堵路追討金門建築近200萬","createTime":"2019-12-19T05:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T20:01:13.000Z","uid":165683,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"848916351cf4797ac9401bbb1f77baae087a254a","tid":1788952,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T05:58:59.000Z","msg":"建築地盤職工總會與13名石矢工及雜工，今早約8時40分到位於海洋公園「水世界」地盤項目出入口示威，他們手持「還我法定假期錢」、「有汗出 無糧出」等橫額，堵塞地盤出入口，追討判商拖欠近200萬人工、代通知金、年假及勞工假期薪金。有金門建築職員約10時45分到場，惟稱仍需再請示上級，現場工友目前仍在等待，並指「冇糧出就唔走」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191219/60394366\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191219%2F60394366&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6kkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=02046254\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191219%2F60394366&h=3cf3f77c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191219/60394366</a>"},{"pid":"72e5ee4da41251f765dbc541353e0bf5f775f2e9","tid":1788952,"uid":6845,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:00:40.000Z","msg":"非法集結 但係唔敢派防暴搞地盤佬"},{"pid":"8b39d49586fb4593ae79a8b1fc237cb2a4d38ff9","tid":1788952,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:01:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2a747f32a592e22e0ecd42aa62181c5d30b56091","tid":1788952,"uid":222970,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:02:35.000Z","msg":"用太空卡報警 話佢地有頭盔 豬咀 即係暴徒搞事"},{"pid":"2b1d895434c93a59e4407e414449ad9da841fbba","tid":1788952,"uid":228143,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:03:22.000Z","msg":"好人好姐點會拖<br />\n<br />\n你唔搞事  人地會拖你？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藍屍金句<br />\n<br />\n自己中晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" cla